Natural language: How many films are in the database?
List all film titles.
generated request:
PREFIX ex: <http://example.org/movies/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT ?title
WHERE {
  ?film rdf:type ex:Film .
  ?film ex:title ?title .
}

Natural language: List all films with their release year.
generated request:
PREFIX ex: <http://example.org/movies/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT ?title ?year
WHERE {
  ?film a ex:Film .
  ?film ex:title ?title .
  ?film ex:year ?year .
}

Natural language: How many actors are there?
List all directors.
List all films released after 2010.
generated request:
PREFIX ex: <http://example.org/movies/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT ?title
WHERE {
    ?film rdf:type ex:Film .
    ?film ex:title ?title .
    ?film ex:year ?year .
    FILTER(?year > 2010)
}

Natural language: List all films longer than 150 minutes.
generated request:
PREFIX ex: <http://example.org/movies/>

SELECT ?title
WHERE {
  ?film a ex:Film .
  ?film ex:duration ?duration .
  ?film ex:title ?title .
  FILTER(?duration > 150)
}

Natural language: Which films were directed and produced by the same person?
generated request:
PREFIX ex: <http://example.org/movies/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

Natural language: Which actors appeared in more than one film?
generated request:
PREFIX ex: <http://example.org/movies/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT ?actorName
WHERE {
  ?film ex:actor ?actor .
  ?actor ex:name ?actorName .
}
GROUP BY ?actorName
HAVING (COUNT(DISTINCT ?film) > 1)
correct request:
PREFIX ex: <http://example.org/movies/>

SELECT ?actor (COUNT(?film) AS ?count)
WHERE {
  ?film ex:actor ?actor .
}
GROUP BY ?actor
HAVING(COUNT(?film) > 1)

Natural language: List all people born before 1970.
generated request:
PREFIX ex: <http://example.org/movies/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>

SELECT ?person ?name
WHERE {
  ?person a ex:Person .
  ?person ex:birthYear ?year .
  ?person ex:name ?name .
  FILTER (?year < 1970)
}

Natural language: List all genres with the number of films per genre.
generated request:
PREFIX ex: <http://example.org/movies/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT ?genre (COUNT(?film) AS ?numberOfFilms)
WHERE {
  ?film ex:hasGenre ?genre .
}
GROUP BY ?genre

Natural language: What is the highest rated film?
generated request:
PREFIX ex: <http://example.org/movies/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT ?title
WHERE {
  ?film a ex:Film .
  ?film ex:rating ?rating .
  ?film ex:title ?title .
}
ORDER BY DESC(?rating)
LIMIT 1

Natural language: List films released between 2000 and 2015.
generated request:

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>

SELECT ?title
WHERE {
  ?film a ex:Film .
